title: Florida golfer used his club to escape from an alligator | Daily Mail Online
text: show ad A putt-ing miracle! Florida golfer used his club to escape from an alligator that had grabbed him by the ankle and pulled him waist-deep into water Tony Aarts used his putter to jab a gator in the eyes after being grabbed by the ankle The Florida man was pulled waist-deep into a water hazard by the alligator The alligator has been captured and put down by wildlife workers Published: 21:06 GMT, 11 February 2017 | Updated: 12:00 GMT, 12 February 2017 173 shares
